data.description: This captivating residence presents a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance, making it an ideal sanctuary for families and individuals seeking a place to call home. Living room boasts vaulted, wood beam ceilings, built-ins, and a brick gas log fireplace. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with modern stainless-steel appliances and ample cabinetry, counter space and coffee bar. A formal dining room creates an excellent space for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with loved ones. The primary suite has a private en suite with garden tub, separate shower, and his & her closets. Additional bedrooms share access to a well-designed secondary bathroom and have walk-in closets. Large back yard with 6 foot wood fence and shed and patio plumbed for gas, perfect for entertaining. The driveway has plenty of room for your boat! Lovely neighborhood near Lake Ray Hubbard and quick access to I30 and George Bush toll road 190. Smart features & security throughout. NO HOA! MUST SEE!
